Step 1: Create graph with edge in direction of increasing Richness.
Step 2: Run DFS on all 0 indegree nodes.
Step 3: Return min value node from dfs method comparing current node quietness value with all child nodes.
Step 4: Use the result array to reduce reprocessing (DP) if the node is already visited.

