To reduce the deviation, we can either increase the minimum value or decrease the maximum value.
Also, based on the conditions, only odd elements can be increased (multiplied by 2) and only even elements can be reduced (divided by 2).

The first loop takes care of increasing the min value to as much as possible and the second loop takes care of decreasing the max value to as much as possible.

