# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
1. Did all odd no. as even by multiplying by 2 and pushing all to priority queue.
2. performing while operation until top element dont become odd,
3. In while we taking top element as `max` then popping it out and pushing its half back in and also checking for `ans` by seeing if `max-min` is less then `ans` or not and also same for `min` if `num/2` gets less then `min` making it `min`.
4. In end returning `ans`.

