# Approach
1. make all odd value even
2. take min of all value
3. find max and difference and update max/2 till the max is even
4. Otherwise differenc is the result 
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->

# Complexity
- Time complexity:O(NlogNlogM)
