<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
Using set, we go through the list and find the minimum Deviation.
# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
1. we iterate the set until we found a even number. when we found odd number we update min value and insert 2*odd into the set.
2. we interate the set from last to first until we found a odd number. when we found a even number we update min value and insert even/2 into the set.
3. copy 1st step. 
# Complexity
- Time complexity:
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
